{
  "debug": false,
  "spacing": 8,
  "padding": [
    20,
    20,
    20,
    20
  ],
  "footer": true,
  "images": false,
  "views": [
    {
      "type": "vStack",
      "spacing": 4,
      "views": [
        {
          "value": "{{name}}",
          "style": "title",
          "alignment": "center"
        },
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "style": "summary",
      "value": "{{data.summary}}",
    }, 
    {
      "type": "image",
      "value": "/images/top-border.png",
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "style": "mechanics-body-white",
      "value": "{% include \"class-primary.md\" %}",
      "bgColor": "#5D0000",
      "padding": [16],
      "borderColor": "#d8c384",
      "borderWidth": 2,
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "{{descr}}",
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "value": "/images/bottom-border.png",
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "## Initial Proficiencies\n\nAt 1st level, you gain the listed proficiency ranks in the following statistics. You are untrained in anything not listed unless you gain a better proficiency rank in some other way.",
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "style": "mechanics-body",
      "value": "{% include \"class-secondary.md\" %}",
      "bgColor": "#ffffff",
      "padding": [16],
      "borderColor": "#cccccc",
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "value": "/images/bottom-border.png",
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "## Class Features\n\nYou gain these abilities as an {{name|lowercase}}. Abilities gained at higher levels list the levels at which you gain them next to the featuresâ€™ names.",
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "attribute": "data.classFeatures",
      "views": [
        {
          "type": "hStack",
          "alignment": "bottom",
          "padding": [8, 0, 0, 0],
          "views": [
            {
              "value": "{{name|uppercase}}",
              "style": "heading3",
            },
            {
              "value": "{% if level > 1 %}{{level|ordinal}}{% endif %}",
              "alignment": "trailing",
              "style": "heading3",
              "width": -1,
            },
          ]
        }, 
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "{{text}}",
        }
      ]
    },
  ]
}